data.description: **OPEN HOUSE Saturday 4/27 1:30-3:30 pm!** Pictures don't do this justice! You must see this home in person to truly appreciate all it has to offer! Great home with fantastic yard & amazing mountain views! Large .31 acre lot is the perfect place to relax and entertain: huge 20'x40' patio, floating 16'x10.5' trex deck, pergola over hot tub pad, pergola for hammocks, garden boxes, 10'x12' shed w/ electrical, and trampoline. Abundant parking: 2 car garage with insulated garage door, and large cement RV pad. Inside, the kitchen features SS appliances, new subway tile backsplash, painted cabinets, & spacious pantry. Newer LVP flooring on main floor (installed 2019). Huge owner's suite w/ large walk-in closet and big bathroom. Large bedrooms with brand new carpet. Loft on the 2nd floor can be used as a second family room or easily be converted into a 4th bedroom. Large living area on the main with a large home office space. Fiber internet available.
